snippet.title: FUNNIEST retro ANIMAL VIDEOS - Prepare yourself to LAUGH HARD!
snippet.description:
Some goldies from our retro libraries. 10, 15 years old clips which are still stunning! It is just another proof that animals keep being amusing throughout all times! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our video, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
